{"tid":2285810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人放棄去人多嘅地方？(壽司郎,就腳露營地點,etc)","createTime":"2020-11-14T12:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T16:08:28.000Z","uid":69157,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12d019d64b95bd7b82a64bbf2d6a641a125a6100","tid":2285810,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"心裡面其實好想食，但都會慢慢等個熱潮過去，或者搵取替品<br />\n與其排隊排咁耐，不如慳時間做其他野<br />\n見到人多就心很累　有時想食一樣野，千山萬水去到先同你講唔好意思兩個鐘後先有位<br />\n逐間打去問，星期五打邊爐，間間都ＦＵＬＬ<br />\n想去露營，一睇D相，嘩屌營貼營....<br />\n想去行山，熱門地點多人過旺角，仲有班大陸口音既人唔帶口罩貼身迎面過來..<br />\n以前萬聖節去LKF, 逼撚到就快比鬼佬插到屎忽<br />\n<br />\n真係太多人啦　屌!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39550bb41fb79e1b730f41c18ad15421c147d2fb","tid":2285810,"uid":69157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人圍爐"},{"pid":"07e51530d78a056a84489775fe47462722da1a75","tid":2285810,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"成個香港都準備放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e53f314693922978a368186869fcca625b18c4","tid":2285810,"uid":372055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"香港真係太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇替代品？"},{"pid":"66404516e1bda03f8917d3cdce792b773138cd1d","tid":2285810,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e51530d78a056a84489775fe47462722da1a75","tid":2285810,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"成個香港都準備放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"留在家中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" clas